{"tid":2307750,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華春瑩：中方沒有使用偽造照片，是中國一名年輕人用電腦繪製的插畫，反映澳洲國防部已經證實的調查報告","createTime":"2020-12-01T11:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T11:15:36.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a3baaea53031d0e970969773d73f5418948079b4","tid":2307750,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:07:56.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部發言人華春瑩再度回應澳洲指責中方使用偽造照片，反駁澳洲的指責本身是虛假，認為澳洲一些人作出令人詫異的強烈反應，真實目的是想轉移視線，企圖把國際輿論對澳洲一些軍人，殘殺阿富汗無辜平民的批評和譴責，轉換成「對華示強」。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩說，網上流傳的不是照片，是中國一名年輕人用電腦繪製的插畫，插畫與偽造照片是不同概念。她又說，插畫的根據，是澳洲國防部已經證實的調查報告，反映的是事實。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩在記者會上，又展示一些從網上列印、外國傳媒有關澳洲國防部的報道和圖片，說這些都是澳洲自己發布的資料。"},{"pid":"ee0723ec3c45fab7825d44298ba12851cb1fed16","tid":2307750,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:08:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"038cb29b6c06a163ee50c7a1702b8e17b85edb58","tid":2307750,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:08:48.000Z","msg":"澳洲都冇PS<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd0e0e66d5ca3e31f7ffda4ed49b7b57c0da8bc","tid":2307750,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d82da0ba20d69db566e688d61c98189d0042fa5","tid":2307750,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:09:48.000Z","msg":"支持趙氏同華氏兩條冚家鏟繼續頂落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ea90c46894a4f3a06ed3da57218fd41b70277a","tid":2307750,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:12:03.000Z","msg":"得啦，知你地聽老細話啦 <img src=\"/asse